PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of MICHAEL O'BRIEN of Summerside, Prince Edward Island, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on February 28, 2009, in the place of Ronald J. Keefe.
